<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.10">
<l>ayarkkuñcuṟ ṟumpaṟṟi nōkku makalavē nīṇōkkuk koḷḷum</l>
<l>viyarkku maḻaikkaṇ ṭuḷumpa vevvuyirk koḷḷumey cōrum</l>
<l>peyarttuṅ kaṇṇā veṉṟu pēcum perumāṉē vāveṉṟu kūvu</l>
<l>mayalperuṅ kātaleṉ pētaik keṉceykēṉ valviṉai yēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She forgets, she looks fixedly all around, she widely casts long glances,</l>
<l>she perspires, while [her] rain eyes brim over, she heaves hot sighs, [her] body faints,</l>
<l>repeatedly she says “o Kaṇṇaṉ”, “o great lord, come”, she cooes.</l>
<l>For my daughter in mad great love, what will I do, I of harsh deeds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
